 :tx/rationale "Create task: EPIC: Metabolic Store — Self-Observing Transactions with Three-Boundary Coherence Vector (INV-STORE-014, INV-BILATERAL-001, INV-HARVEST-005, INV-SEED-001). BACKGROUND: The store is currently passive — datoms go in, nothing comes out unless the agent asks. Every process obligation (observe, harvest, reconcile, audit) is a ceremony the agent must remember, and ceremonies decay under pressure (SEED.md §5). The metabolic store inverts this: transact() becomes self-aware, annotating every transaction with semantic metadata that downstream systems (urgency, routing, seed, F(S)) query incrementally instead of computing from scratch. The fundamental insight: the system has four epistemological layers (Intent→Spec→Impl→Behavior) connected by three boundaries. The coherence state is fully characterized by per-transaction delta measurements at each boundary: delta-crystallization (Intent↔Spec), delta-implementation (Spec↔Impl), delta-verification (Impl↔Behavior). These three deltas form the complete metabolic signature — they tell you where knowledge is stuck in the pipeline. HEBBIAN-BAYESIAN SYNTHESIS: Bottom-up (Hebbian) = entities co-occurring in high-novelty transactions get stronger associations. Top-down (Bayesian) = seed assembles prior, transactions provide evidence, coherence-delta measures prediction error. One builds the map, the other navigates it. APPROACH: Phase 1: delta-crystallization (only boundary with zero existing coverage). Phase 2: Real-time crystallization feedback in braid observe output. Phase 3: Harvest-integrated reconciliation using delta data. Phase 4: delta-implementation + delta-verification. Phase 5: Downstream integration (urgency, routing, seed, session progress). AXIOLOGICAL ALIGNMENT: SEED.md §7 promises three things improve with use (graph densifies, instructions adapt, heuristics sharpen). Currently aspirational. Metabolic transactions make all three continuous and structural — the system cannot avoid improving. ACCEPTANCE: (A) Every transaction gains semantic metadata datoms. (B) braid observe shows crystallization feedback in real time. (C) Harvest auto-closes store-verifiable tasks. (D) F(S) updates incrementally. (E) Alert fatigue eliminated. TRACES TO: INV-STORE-014, INV-BILATERAL-001, INV-BILATERAL-002, INV-HARVEST-001, INV-HARVEST-005, INV-SEED-001, INV-GUIDANCE-014, INV-GUIDANCE-019, INV-GUIDANCE-024, ADR-GUIDANCE-002."
